    {
      "start": 255.28,
      "end": 255.54,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 255.54,
      "end": 257.78,
      "text": "Sometimes when things seem too good to be true"
    },
    {
      "start": 257.78,
      "end": 259.28,
      "text": "you wonder if you're dreaming"
    },
    {
      "start": 259.28,
      "end": 260.68,
      "text": "or is this reality"
    },
    {
      "start": 260.68,
      "end": 263.68,
      "text": "or what are this person's intentions"
    },
    {
      "start": 263.68,
      "end": 265.22,
      "text": "what is happening?"
    },
    {
      "start": 265.46,
      "end": 265.62,
      "text": "그렇죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 265.62,
      "end": 266.14,
      "text": "그래서"
    },
    {
      "start": 266.14,
      "end": 268.74,
      "text": "항상 너무 좋은 일들이 일어나면"
    },
    {
      "start": 268.74,
      "end": 271.26,
      "text": "그건 현실성이 없다라는 의미로"
    },
    {
      "start": 271.26,
      "end": 274.12,
      "text": "I know when things seem too good to be true"
    },
    {
      "start": 274.12,
      "end": 275.5,
      "text": "라는 표현을 활용을 한 겁니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 275.5,
      "end": 278.32,
      "text": "I think the only thing you need to know"
